#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:140
#, no-c-format
msgid "The elements of the default user interface are:"
msgstr "Voici les éléments de l'interface utilisateur par défaut :"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:145
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The toolbar, which can be used for quick access to frequently used actions. "
"The toolbar can be customized by clicking it with the &RMB; and choosing "
"<menuchoice><guimenuitem>Configure Toolbars...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> "
"from the context menu, with <guimenuitem>Configure Toolbars...</guimenuitem> "
"from the <guibutton>Control</guibutton> button at the right of the toolbar "
"or via <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure "
"Toolbars...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> from the main menu."
msgstr ""
"La barre d'outils, qu'on peut utiliser pour un accès rapide aux actions "
"courantes. Il est possible de la personnaliser en cliquant dessus avec le "
"&BDS; et en choisissant <menuchoice><guimenuitem>Configurer les barres "
"d'outils...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> depuis le menu contextuel, avec "
"<guimenuitem>Configurer les barres d'outils...</guimenuitem> à partir du "
"bouton <guibutton>Contrôle</guibutton> situé à droite de la barre d'outils "
"ou via <menuchoice><guimenu>Configuration</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configurer "
"les barres d'outils...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> depuis le menu principal."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:156 index.docbook:267 index.docbook:297
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of &dolphin;'s toolbar"
msgstr "Capture d'écran de la barre d'outils de &dolphin;"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid "The default toolbar."
msgstr "La barre d'outils par défaut."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:165
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Toolbar items where the icon is sufficient for knowing the command do not "
#| "have a text alongside the icons. This can be changed by a &RMB; click and "
#| "selecting the item text below <guilabel>Show Text</guilabel>. The "
#| "<guibutton>Control</guibutton> button at the right side of the toolbar is "
#| "only displayed if the menubar is hidden."
msgid ""
"Toolbar items where the icon is sufficient for knowing the command do not "
"have text alongside the icons. This can be changed by a &RMB; click and "
"selecting the item text below <guilabel>Show Text</guilabel>. The "
"<guibutton>Control</guibutton> button at the right side of the toolbar is "
"only displayed if the menubar is hidden."
msgstr ""
"Les éléments de barre d'outils, où l'icône est suffisante pour connaître la "
"commande ne comportent pas de texte à côté des icônes. On peut modifier ce "
"comportement en cliquant avec le &BDS; et en sélectionnant le texte de "
"l'élément situé sous <guilabel>Afficher le texte</guilabel>. Le bouton "
"<guibutton>Contrôle</guibutton> situé sur le côté droit de la barre d'outils "
"n'est affiché que si la barre de menus est cachée."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The location bar, which always displays the path to the current folder. It "
"can be switched between two different modes, see the <link linkend="
"\"location-bar\">section on the location bar</link> for details."
msgstr ""
"La barre d'emplacement, affichant toujours l'emplacement du dossier actuel. "
"Elle peut basculer entre deux modes différents. Consultez la <link linkend="
"\"location-bar\">section sur la barre d'emplacement</link> pour plus de "
"détails."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:182
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <link linkend=\"dolphin-view\">view</link>, which shows all files and "
"folders in the current folder."
msgstr ""
"La <link linkend=\"dolphin-view\">vue</link>, affichant tous les fichiers et "
"dossiers présents dans le dossier actuel."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:187
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The <link linkend=\"places-panel\"><guilabel>Places</guilabel> panel</"
#| "link>, which provides quick access to bookmarked locations and disks or "
#| "other media. A &RMB; click opens the context menu to edit, add, hide or "
#| "remove entries."
msgid ""
"The <link linkend=\"places-panel\"><guilabel>Places</guilabel> panel</link>, "
"which provides quick access to bookmarked locations and disks or other media."
msgstr ""
"Le <link linkend=\"places-panel\">panneau <guilabel>Emplacements</guilabel></"
"link>, fournissant un accès rapide aux emplacements mis en signets, ainsi "
"qu'aux disques ou à d'autres média. Un clic avec le &BDS; ouvre le menu "
"contextuel pour modifier, ajouter, cacher ou supprimer des éléments."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:191
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If desktop search and file indexing are enabled in the <guilabel>Desktop "
"Search</guilabel> module in the &systemsettings; the panel provides "
"<guilabel>Recent</guilabel> items and allows you to search for "
"<guilabel>Documents</guilabel>, <guilabel>Images</guilabel>, <guilabel>Audio "
"Files</guilabel> and <guilabel>Video</guilabel>."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:197
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The status bar. It displays the name, size and type of the file which is "
#| "currently hovered with the mouse, or the number and size of the files "
#| "which are selected. At the right, there is a zoom slider that permits to "
#| "adjust the size of the icons in the view."
msgid ""
"The status bar. It displays the name, size and type of the file which is "
"currently hovered over with the mouse, or the number and size of the files "
"which are selected. At the right, there is a zoom slider that allows you to "
"adjust the size of the icons in the view."
msgstr ""
"La barre d'état, affichant le nom, la taille et le type du fichier sur "
"lequel passe actuellement la souris ou le nombre et la taille des fichiers "
"sélectionnés. À droite, se trouve un curseur de zoom qui permet d'ajuster la "
"taille des icônes dans la vue."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:204
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The menu bar (hidden by default), which provides access to all commands "
#| "and configuration options. See the <link linkend=\"commands-menubar"
#| "\">Command Reference</link> for a list of all menu commands. The menu bar "
#| "can be toggled with <guimenuitem>Show Menubar</guimenuitem> from the "
#| "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> menu or the <guibutton>Control</guibutton> "
#| "button (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>M</keycap></keycombo>)."
msgid ""
"The menubar (hidden by default), which provides access to all commands and "
"configuration options. See the <link linkend=\"commands-menubar\">Command "
"Reference</link> for a list of all menu commands. The menubar can be toggled "
"with <guimenuitem>Show Menubar</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl;<keycap>M</keycap></keycombo>) from the <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
"menu or the <guibutton>Control</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"La barre de menus (cachée par défaut), fournissant l'accès à toutes les "
"commandes et options de configuration. Consultez la section <link linkend="
"\"commands-menubar\">Référence des commandes</link> pour obtenir une liste "
"de toutes les commandes des menus. On peut (dés)activer la barre de menus "
"avec <guimenuitem>Afficher la barre de menus</guimenuitem> depuis le menu "
"<guimenu>Configuration</guimenu> ou le bouton <guibutton>Contrôle</"
"guibutton> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>M</keycap></keycombo>)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:211
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the menubar is hidden, all its actions are available from the "
"<guibutton>Control</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:215
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The additional <guilabel>Information</guilabel>, <guilabel>Folders</"
#| "guilabel>, <guilabel>Terminal</guilabel> and <guilabel>Search</guilabel> "
#| "panels are hidden by default, for more information see <link linkend="
#| "\"panels\"><guilabel>Panels</guilabel>.</link>"
msgid ""
"The additional <guilabel>Information</guilabel>, <guilabel>Folders</"
"guilabel> and <guilabel>Terminal</guilabel> panels are hidden by default, "
"for more information see <link linkend=\"panels\"><guilabel>Panels</"
"guilabel>.</link>"
msgstr ""
"Les panneaux addtionnels <guilabel>Informations</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Dossiers</guilabel>, <guilabel>Terminal</guilabel> et "
"<guilabel>Recherche</guilabel> sont cachés par défaut. Pour plus "
"d'informations, consultez la section <link linkend=\"panels"
"\"><guilabel>Panneaux</guilabel>.</link>"

