"<guimenuitem>Droits d'accès</guimenuitem>, le <guimenuitem>Propriétaire</"
"guimenuitem>, le <guimenuitem>Groupe</guimenuitem>, le <guimenuitem>Type</"
"guimenuitem>, la <guimenuitem>Destination du lien</guimenuitem> ou "
"l'<guimenuitem>Emplacement</guimenuitem> dans les différentes vues."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:421
#, no-c-format
msgid "Preview"
msgstr "Aperçu"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:423
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If <guibutton>Preview</guibutton> is enabled, the icons are based on the "
#| "actual file or folder contents. E.g., for images a scaled down preview of "
#| "the image is shown."
msgid ""
"If <guibutton>Preview</guibutton> is enabled, the icons are based on the "
"actual file or folder contents; &eg; for images a scaled down preview of the "
"image is shown."
msgstr ""
"Si on clique sur le bouton <guibutton>Aperçu</guibutton>, les icônes "
"reposent sur le contenu réel des fichiers ou des dossiers. Par exemple, pour "
"les images, un aperçu réduit de l'image est affiché."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:432
#, no-c-format
msgid "Split"
msgstr "Scinder"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:434
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If <guibutton>Split</guibutton> is clicked, two views are shown which can "
"display the contents of different folders. This can be convenient for moving "
"or copying files."
msgstr ""
"Si on clique sur le bouton <guibutton>Scinder</guibutton>, deux vues sont "
"présentées, ce qui permet d'afficher le contenu de différents dossiers. "
"Cette fonction peut être pratique pour déplacer ou copier des fichiers."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:445
#, no-c-format
msgid "Selecting Items in the View"
msgstr "Sélectionner des éléments dans la vue"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:447
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are several ways to select items in the view. Once a group of items is "
"selected, all actions, such as <menuchoice><guimenuitem>Cut</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>, <menuchoice><guimenuitem>Copy</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, "
"<menuchoice><guimenuitem>Move to Trash</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, and drag "
"and drop operations, affect all selected items."
msgstr ""
"Il existe plusieurs façons de sélectionner des éléments dans la vue. Dès "
"l'instant où un groupe d'éléments est sélectionné, toutes les actions telles "
"que <menuchoice><guimenuitem>Couper</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, "
"<menuchoice><guimenuitem>Copier</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, "
"<menuchoice><guimenuitem>Mettre à la corbeille</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, "
"ainsi que les opérations de glisser-déposer, affectent tous les éléments "
"sélectionnés."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:457
#, no-c-format
msgid "Selecting Items Using the Mouse"
msgstr "Sélectionner des éléments à l'aide de la souris"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:461
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can press the &LMB; somewhere in the view and draw a rectangle around a "
"group of items before releasing the button. This will select all items in "
"the rectangle and clear the previous selection. If the &Shift; key is "
"pressed during the selection process, the previous selection is kept."
msgstr ""
"On peut cliquer avec le &BGS; dans un endroit quelconque de la vue et tracer "
"un rectangle autour d'un groupe d'éléments avant de relâcher le bouton. "
"Cette action sélectionnera tous les éléments contenus dans le rectangle et "
"effacera la sélection précédente. Si on appuie sur la touche &Maj; pendant "
"le processus de sélection, la sélection précédente est conservée."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:468
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the &Ctrl; key is pressed while an item is clicked with the &LMB;, the "
"selection state of this item is toggled. If the &Ctrl; key is pressed while "
"a rectangle is drawn around a group of items as described above, the "
"selection state of all items in the rectangle will be toggled."
msgstr ""
"Si on appuie sur la touche &Ctrl; alors qu'on a cliqué sur un élément avec "
"le &BGS;, l'état de la sélection de cet élément est (dés)activé. Si on "
"appuie sur la touche &Ctrl; alors qu'un rectangle est tracé autour d'un "
"groupe d'éléments comme décrit ci-dessus, l'état de la sélection de tous les "
"éléments contenus dans le rectangle sera (dés)activé."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:475
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the &Shift; key is pressed while an item is clicked with the &LMB;, all "
"items between the previous current item and the clicked item will be "
"selected."
msgstr ""
"Si on appuie sur la touche &Maj; alors qu'on a cliqué sur un élément avec le "
"&BGS;, tous les éléments se trouvant entre l'élément actuel et l'élément "
"cliqué seront sélectionnés."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:480
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If <guilabel>Show selection marker</guilabel> is enabled in the <link "
#| "linkend=\"preferences-dialog-general-behavior\"><quote>Behavior</quote> "
#| "tab of the <guilabel>General</guilabel> section of the settings</link>, a "
#| "small <guiicon>+</guiicon> or <guiicon>-</guiicon> button appears in the "
#| "top left corner of the item which is currently hovered with the mouse. "
#| "Clicking this sign selects or deselects the item, respectively."
msgid ""
"If <guilabel>Show selection marker</guilabel> is enabled in the <link "
"linkend=\"preferences-dialog-general-behavior\"><quote>Behavior</quote> tab "
"of the <guilabel>General</guilabel> section of the settings</link>, a small "
"<guiicon>+</guiicon> or <guiicon>-</guiicon> button appears in the top left "
"corner of the item which is currently hovered over with the mouse. Clicking "
"this sign selects or deselects the item, respectively."
msgstr ""
"Si <guilabel>Afficher l'indicateur de sélection</guilabel> est coché dans "
"l'<link linkend=\"preferences-dialog-general-behavior\">onglet "
"<quote>Comportement</quote> de la section <guilabel>Général</guilabel> des "
"préférences</link>, un petit bouton <guiicon>+</guiicon> ou <guiicon>-</"
"guiicon> apparaît dans le coin supérieur gauche de l'élément sur lequel la "
"souris passe actuellement. Cliquer sur ce signe sélectionne ou désélectionne "
"l'élément, respectivement."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:494
#, no-c-format
msgid "Selecting Items Using the Keyboard"
msgstr "Sélectionner des éléments à l'aide du clavier"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:498
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If an arrow key, <keycap>Page Up</keycap>, <keycap>Page Down</keycap>, "
"<keycap>Home</keycap>, or <keycap>End</keycap> is pressed, the new current "
"item is selected, and the previous selection is cleared."
msgstr ""
"Si on appuie sur une touche fléchée, <keycap>Page précédente</keycap>, "
"<keycap>Page suivante</keycap>, <keycap>Début</keycap> ou <keycap>Fin</"
"keycap>, le nouvel élément actuel est sélectionné et la sélection précédente "
"effacée."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:504
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the &Ctrl; key is held while one of the above keys is pressed, the "
"selection remains unchanged."
msgstr ""
"Si on maintient enfoncée la touche &Ctrl; tout en appuyant sur les touches "
"ci-dessus, la sélection reste inchangée."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:509
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the &Shift; key is held while one of the above keys is pressed, all items "
"between the previous current item and the new current item will be selected."
msgstr ""
"Si on maintient enfoncée la touche &Maj; tout en appuyant sur l'une des "
"touches ci-dessus, tous les éléments se trouvant entre le précédent élément "
"actuel et le nouvel élément actuel seront sélectionnés."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:514
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keysym>Space</keysym></keycombo> is "
"pressed, the selection state of the current item is toggled."
msgstr ""
"Si on appuie sur <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keysym>Espace</keysym></"
"keycombo>, l'état de la sélection de l'élément actuel est (dés)activé."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:519
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>A</keycap></keycombo> selects all "
"items in the view."
msgstr ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>A</keycap></keycombo> sélectionne "
"tous les éléments dans la vue."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:524
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>A</keycap></keycombo> "
"toggles the selection state of all items in the view."
msgstr ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Maj;<keycap>A</keycap></keycombo> "
"(dés)active l'état de la sélection de tous les éléments figurant dans la vue."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:529
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Select a file or folder by typing the first few letters of its name and "
#| "the the first matching item is selected. To clear the selection and "
#| "cancel the keyboard search press &Esc; or wait longer than the timeout of "
#| "1 second."
msgid ""
"Select a file or folder by typing the first few letters of its name and the "
"first matching item is selected. To clear the selection and cancel the "
"keyboard search press &Esc; or wait longer than the timeout of 1 second."
msgstr ""
"Sélectionnez un fichier ou un dossier en saisissant les premières lettres de "
"son nom, et le premier élément correspondant sera sélectionné. Pour effacer "
"la sélection et annuler la recherche sur le clavier, appuyez sur &Echap; ou "
"attendez plus que le temps imparti d'une seconde."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:547
#, no-c-format
msgid "Location Bar"
msgstr "Barre d'emplacement"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:549
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The location bar, which can be found on top of &dolphin;'s view, displays "
#| "the path to the current folder. The location bar has two modes."
msgid ""
"The location bar, which can be found above &dolphin;'s view, displays the "
"path to the current folder. The location bar has two modes."
msgstr ""
"La barre d'emplacement, qui se trouve en haut de la vue de &dolphin;, "
"affiche l'emplacement du dossier actuel. Elle comporte deux modes."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:555
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bread Crumb Mode"
msgstr "Mode <quote>fil d'Ariane</quote>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:557
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "In the <quote>bread crumb</quote> mode, which is the default, each folder "
#| "name in the path to the current folder is a button which can be clicked "
#| "to quickly open that folder. Moreover, clicking the <quote>&gt;</quote> "
#| "sign to the right of a folder opens a menu which permits to quickly open "
#| "a subfolder of that folder."
msgid ""
"In the <quote>bread crumb</quote> mode, which is the default, each folder "
"name in the path to the current folder is a button which can be clicked to "
"quickly open that folder. Moreover, clicking the <quote>&gt;</quote> sign to "
"the right of a folder opens a menu which allows you to quickly open a "
"subfolder of that folder."
msgstr ""
"En mode <quote>fil d'Ariane</quote>, le réglage par défaut, chaque nom de "
"dossier dans l'emplacement du dossier actuel est un bouton sur lequel on "
"peut cliquer pour ouvrir rapidement ce dossier. De plus, cliquer sur le "
"signe <quote>&gt;</quote> situé à droite d'un dossier ouvre un menu "
"permettant d'ouvrir rapidement un sous-dossier de ce dossier."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:565
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the location bar in bread crumb mode"
msgstr ""
"Capture d'écran de la barre d'emplacement en mode <quote>fil d'Ariane</quote>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:571
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Location bar in bread crumb mode.</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Barre d'emplacement en mode <quote>fil d'Ariane</quote>.</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:573
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Location bar in bread crumb mode.</para>"
msgstr "<para>Barre d'emplacement en mode <quote>fil d'Ariane</quote>.</para>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:580
#, no-c-format
msgid "Editable Mode"
msgstr "Mode <quote>modifiable</quote>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:582
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "When in bread crumb mode, clicking in the grey area to the right of the "
#| "path with the &LMB; switches the location bar to the <quote>editable</"
#| "quote> mode, in which the path can be edited using the keyboard. To "
#| "switch back to bread crumb mode, click the check mark at the right of the "
#| "location bar with the &LMB;."
msgid ""
"When in bread crumb mode, clicking in the gray area to the right of the path "
"with the &LMB; switches the location bar to <quote>editable</quote> mode, in "
"which the path can be edited using the keyboard. To switch back to bread "
"crumb mode, click the check mark at the right of the location bar with the "
"&LMB;."
msgstr ""
"En mode <quote>fil d'Ariane</quote>, cliquer dans la zone grisée située à "
"droite de l'emplacement avec le &BGS; fait basculer la barre d'emplacement "
"en mode <quote>modifiable</quote>, dans lequel on peut chang er "
"l'emplacement à l'aide du clavier. Pour revenir au mode <quote>fil d'Ariane</"
"quote>, cliquez avec le &BDS; sur la case à cocher située à droite de la "
"barre d'emplacement."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:590
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the location bar in editable mode"
msgstr ""
"Capture d'écran de la barre d'emplacement en mode <quote>modifiable</quote>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:596
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Location bar in editable mode.</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Barre d'emplacement en mode <quote>modifiable</quote>.</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:598
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Location bar in editable mode.</para>"
msgstr "<para>Barre d'emplacement en mode <quote>modifiable</quote>.</para>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:603
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using Kioslaves"
msgstr "Utilisation des modules d'entrées / sorties."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:605
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the location bar is empty in editable mode, a drop down box appears in "
"front of the bar listing all available kioslaves on your system. Kioslaves "
"are programs built into &kde; which add support for many different protocols "
"to &dolphin; and other &kde; applications."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:610
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For example with the <quote>fish</quote> kioslave &dolphin; can be used to "
"manage files and folders on a remote host that is accessible via "
"<acronym>SSH</acronym>. To do this you would type <userinput>fish://"
"username@remotehost</userinput> into the location bar. Similar remote file "
"management can be done on remote hosts accessible via the &FTP;, &NFS;, "
"SFTP, &SMB; (&CIFS;) or webdav protocols."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:616
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is also possible to use the kioslaves drop down box to access "
"&systemsettings;, fonts, trash, other programs and devices attached to your "
"computer. See the drop down box for the full list of capabilities available "
"from kioslaves on your system."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:621
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the list of kioslaves"
msgstr "Copie d'écran de la liste des modules d'entrées / sorties disponibles."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:627
#, no-c-format
msgid "Location bar showing list of available kioslaves."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:629
#, no-c-format
msgid "List of available kioslaves."
msgstr "Liste des modules d'entrées / sorties disponibles."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:637
#, no-c-format
msgid "Places and Context"
msgstr "Emplacements et Contexte"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:639
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the <guilabel>Places</guilabel> panel is hidden; in both modes an "
"additional icon in front of the path is displayed. This icon can be clicked "
"with the &LMB; to open a menu which offers quick access to <quote>places</"
"quote> and storage media. See the <link linkend=\"places-panel\">section "
"about the Places Panel</link> for details."
msgstr ""
"Si le panneau <guilabel>Emplacements</guilabel> est caché : dans les deux "
"modes, une icône supplémentaire est affichée devant l'emplacement. On peut "
"cliquer sur cette icône avec le &BGS; pour ouvrir un menu offrant un accès "
"rapide à des <quote>emplacements</quote> et à des média de stockage. "
"Consultez la <link linkend=\"places-panel\"> section sur le panneau "
"Emplacements</link> pour plus de détails."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:647
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Location bar with Places icon</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Barre d'emplacement avec l'icône <quote>Emplacements</quote></"
"screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:653
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Location bar with Places icon</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Barre d'emplacement avec l'icône <quote>Emplacements</quote></phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:658
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The context menu of the location bar offers action to switch between the "
#| "modes and to copy and paste the path using the clipboard. Check the last "
#| "option in this context menu to display either the full path starting with "
#| "the root folder of the file system or to display the path starting with "
#| "the current places entry."
msgid ""
"The context menu of the location bar offers actions to switch between the "
"modes and to copy and paste the path using the clipboard. Check the last "
"option in this context menu to display either the full path starting with "
"the root folder of the file system or to display the path starting with the "
"current places entry."
msgstr ""
"Le menu contextuel de la barre d'emplacement offre une action pour basculer "
"entre les modes, ainsi que pour copier et coller l'emplacement à l'aide du "
"presse-papiers. Cochez la dernière option dans ce menu contextuel pour "
"afficher soit l'emplacement complet en partant du dossier racine du système "
"de fichiers, soit l'emplacement en commençant par l'élément des emplacements "
"actuels."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:665
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Location bar context menu</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Menu contextuel de la barre d'emplacement</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:671
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Location bar context menu</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Menu contextuel de la barre d'emplacement</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:681
#, no-c-format
msgid "Panels"
msgstr "Panneaux"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:683
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&dolphin; allows a number of panels to be placed next to the view. These "
#| "can be enabled in <menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu><guisubmenu>Panels</"
#| "guisubmenu></menuchoice>. By unlocking the panels and clicking and "
#| "dragging a panel title, the panel can be moved to a different position, "
#| "even outside the window."
msgid ""
"&dolphin; allows a number of panels to be placed next to the view. These can "
"be enabled in <menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu><guisubmenu>Show Panels</"
"guisubmenu></menuchoice>. By unlocking the panels and clicking and dragging "
"a panel title, the panel can be moved to a different position, even outside "
"the window."
msgstr ""
"&dolphin; permet de placer un certain nombre de panneaux près de la vue. On "
"peut les activer dans <menuchoice><guimenu>Affichage</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Panneaux</guisubmenu></menuchoice>. En déverrouillant "
"les panneaux et à l'aide d'un glisser-déposer sur un titre de panneau, on "
"peut déplacer le panneau en question dans une position différente, même en "
"dehors de la fenêtre."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:691
#, no-c-format
msgid "Places"
msgstr "Emplacements"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:695
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The <guilabel>Places</guilabel> panel is located at the left of the "
#| "window by default. The <guilabel>Places</guilabel> panel shows any "
#| "locations you have bookmarked. It also shows any disk or media attached "
#| "to the computer."
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Places</guilabel> panel is located at the left of the window "
"by default. The <guilabel>Places</guilabel> panel shows any locations you "
"have bookmarked. It also shows any disk or media attached to the computer, "
"recently accessed items and allows you to search for certain type of files. "
"The order of these entries can be changed by drag and drop."
msgstr ""
"Le panneau <guilabel>Emplacements</guilabel> se trouve à gauche de la "
"fenêtre par défaut. Il affiche tout emplacement mis en signet, ainsi que "
"tous les disques ou média raccordés à l'ordinateur."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:702
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The easiest way to add a folder to the <guilabel>Places</guilabel> panel "
#| "is to drag it and drop it in the panel. Moreover, you can click inside "
#| "the panel with the &RMB; and choose <menuchoice><guimenuitem>Add Entry..."
#| "</guimenuitem></menuchoice> from the context menu."
msgid ""
"The easiest way to add a folder to the <guilabel>Places</guilabel> panel is "
"to drag it and drop it in the panel. Moreover, you can click inside the "
"panel with the &RMB; and choose <menuchoice><guimenuitem>Add Entry...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> from the context menu. The first procedure creates "
"a system wide bookmark, the second procedure can be used to add the current "
"path of the location bar or any desired folder or device. A dialog opens "
"where label, location and icon can be edited and the usage of this entry can "
"be restricted to &dolphin;."
msgstr ""
"Le moyen le plus simple d'ajouter un dossier au panneau "
"<guilabel>Emplacements</guilabel> consiste à le glisser-déposer dans le "
"panneau. En outre, on peut cliquer à l'intérieur du panneau avec le &BDS; et "
"choisir <menuchoice><guimenuitem>Ajouter un élément...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> depuis le menu contextuel."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:712
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A &RMB; click opens the context menu to edit, add, hide or remove entries "
"and change the icon size to one of the predefined values or lock/unlock the "
"panels."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:715
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The context menu has an action to open the entry in a new tab. Devices can "
"be unmounted using the context menu."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:721
#, no-c-format
msgid "Information"
msgstr "Informations"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:723
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The <guilabel>Information</guilabel> panel shows extended information "
#| "about the selected items(s) or about of the current folder or the file "
#| "which is currently hovered with the mouse, including size, type, and date "
#| "of last modification. It also features a large preview of the selected "
#| "item and permits to assign a rating, tags, and comments to it."
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Information</guilabel> panel shows extended information about "
"the selected items(s) or about the current folder or the file which is "
"currently hovered over with the mouse, including size, type, and date of "
"last modification. It also features a large preview of the selected item and "
"allows you to assign a rating, tags, and comments to it."
msgstr ""
"Le panneau <guilabel>informations</guilabel> affiche des informations "
"détaillées sur le ou les éléments sélectionnés, sur le dossier actuel ou le "
"fichier sur lequel la souris passe actuellement, y compris la taille, le "
"type et la date de dernière modification. Il comporte également un grand "
"aperçu de l'élément sélectionné et permet de lui attribuer une note, des "
"étiquettes et des commentaires."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:734
#, no-c-format
msgid "Folders"
msgstr "Dossiers"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:736
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Folders</guilabel> panel shows a tree view structure of the "
"file system. It only shows folders. Clicking a folder with the &LMB; opens "
"this folder in the &dolphin; view."
msgstr ""
"Le panneau <guilabel>Dossiers</guilabel> affiche une structure de vue en "
"arbre du système de fichiers. Il ne présente que les dossiers. Cliquer sur "
"un dossier avec le &BGS; ouvre ce dossier dans la vue de &dolphin;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:741
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use <guilabel>Limit to Home Directory</guilabel> to hide all folders from "
"the tree view except your <guilabel>Home</guilabel>."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:747
#, no-c-format
msgid "Terminal"
msgstr "Terminal"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:749
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "This panel contains a terminal. The terminal will open at the folder "
#| "currently shown in the &dolphin; view. Changing the folder in the active "
#| "&dolphin; view will update the working folder of the terminal. The "
#| "terminal only works with local media. Note: Changing folder in the "
#| "terminal will not affect the &dolphin; view."
msgid ""
"This panel contains a terminal. The terminal will open at the folder "
"currently shown in the &dolphin; view. Changing the folder in the active "
"&dolphin; view will update the working folder of the terminal. Changing the "
"directory in the terminal will update the working folder in the &dolphin; "
"view. The terminal only works with local media."
msgstr ""
"Ce panneau contient un terminal qui s'ouvre sur le dossier actuellement "
"affiché dans la vue de &dolphin;. Changer de dossier dans la vue active de "
"&dolphin; mettra à jour le dossier de travail du terminal. Ce dernier ne "
"fonctionne qu'avec des média locaux. Remarque : changer de dossier dans le "
"terminal n'affectera pas la vue de &dolphin;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:762
#, no-c-format
msgid "Quick Tips"
msgstr "Astuces rapides"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:764
#, no-c-format
msgid "The following are a number of tips to save time when using &dolphin;."
msgstr ""
"Vous trouverez ci-dessous un certain nombre d'astuces permettant de gagner "
"du temps lorsqu'on utilise &dolphin;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:769
#, no-c-format
msgid "Quick Bookmarking"
msgstr "Ajouter rapidement des signets"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:771
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To quickly create a bookmark in the <guilabel>Places</guilabel> panel for "
#| "the current folder, right click in the work space and click "
#| "<menuchoice><guimenuitem>Add to Places</guimenuitem></menuchoice> in the "
#| "context menu."
msgid ""
"To quickly create a bookmark in the <guilabel>Places</guilabel> panel for "
"the current folder, &RMB; click in the work space and click "
"<menuchoice><guimenuitem>Add to Places</guimenuitem></menuchoice> in the "
"context menu."
msgstr ""
"Pour créer rapidement un signet dans le panneau <guilabel>Emplacements</"
"guilabel> pour le dossier actuel, cliquez avec le bouton droit dans l'espace "
"de travail et cliquez sur <menuchoice><guimenuitem>Ajouter aux emplacements "
"appropriés</guimenuitem></menuchoice> dans le menu contextuel."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:778
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The corresponding menu item visibility can be toggled via the <link linkend="
"\"preferences-dialog-context-menu\">&dolphin; context menu settings</link>."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:787
#, no-c-format
msgid "Filtering Files"
msgstr "Filtrer des fichiers"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:789
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&dolphin; is capable of filtering files, &ie;, showing only those items "
#| "in the view whose name contains a given text. For example, if you wish to "
#| "show only the <acronym>MP3</acronym> files within a folder, you could "
#| "filter for <quote>.mp3</quote>. This would then filter out all files "
#| "whose name does not contain <quote>.mp3</quote>."
msgid ""
"&dolphin; is capable of filtering files, &ie; showing only those items in "
"the view whose name contains a given text. For example, if you wish to show "
"only the <acronym>MP3</acronym> files within a folder, you could filter for "
"<quote>.mp3</quote>. This would then filter out all files whose name does "
"not contain <quote>.mp3</quote>."
msgstr ""
"&dolphin; est capable de filtrer des fichiers, &cad; n'afficher que ces "
"éléments, présents dans la vue, dont le nom contient un texte donné. Par "
"exemple, si on souhaite afficher uniquement les fichiers <acronym>MP3</"
"acronym> dans un dossier, il est possible de créer un filtre pour <quote>."
"mp3</quote>. Seront alors filtrés tous les fichiers dont le nom ne contient "
"pas <quote>.mp3</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:796
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To filter files, first enable the filter bar, either by pressing "
#| "<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>I</keycap></keycombo> or via the "
#| "menu: <menuchoice> <guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Filter Bar</"
#| "guimenuitem> </menuchoice>. You can then enter the text to be filtered in "
#| "the filter bar. The filter bar can be disabled either by pressing &Esc;, "
#| "or with a &LMB; click on the <guiicon>Hide Filter Bar</guiicon> icon."
msgid ""
"To filter files, first enable the filter bar, either by pressing <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>I</keycap></keycombo> or via the menu: "
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Filter...</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice>. You can then enter the text to be filtered for in the filter "
"bar. The filter bar can be disabled either by pressing &Esc;, or with a "
"&LMB; click on the <guiicon>Hide Filter Bar</guiicon> icon."
msgstr ""
"Pour filtrer des fichiers, activez d'abord la barre de filtre, soit en "
"appuyant sur <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>I</keycap></keycombo> "
"depuis le menu <menuchoice> <guimenu>Outils</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Afficher "
"la barre de filtre</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>. Vous pouvez ensuite saisir "
"le texte à filtrer dans la barre de filtre. On peut afficher cette dernière "
"soit en appuyant sur &Echap;, soit à l'aide d'un clic du &BGS; sur l'icône "
"<guiicon>Cacher la barre de filtre</guiicon>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:807
#, no-c-format
msgid "Finding Files and Searching in Files"
msgstr "Chercher des fichiers et chercher dans des fichiers"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:810
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&dolphin; is capable of searching for files and for content in files. If "
#| "<keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Ctrl;<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo> is "
#| "pressed or <menuchoice> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Find...</"
#| "guimenuitem> </menuchoice> is used, the <guilabel>Find</guilabel> bar "
#| "will open already set up to search for files within the current folder "
#| "and any sub-folders. Start to type into the find input box and the search "
#| "starts immediately."
msgid ""
"&dolphin; is capable of searching for files and for content in files. If "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Ctrl;<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo> is pressed "
"or <menuchoice> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Search...</guimenuitem> "
"</menuchoice> is used, the <guilabel>Search</guilabel> bar will open already "
"set up to search for files within the current folder and any sub-folders. "
"Start to type into the find input box and the search starts immediately."
msgstr ""
"&dolphin; est capable de chercher des fichiers et du contenu dans des "
"fichiers. Lorsqu'on appuie sur <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>F</"
"keycap></keycombo> ou qu'on utilise le menu <menuchoice><guimenu>Édition</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Chercher...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, la barre "
"<guilabel>Chercher</guilabel> s'ouvre, déjà configurée pour effectuer une "
"recherche de fichers dans le dossier actuel et n'importe quel sous-dossier. "
"Commencez à saisir dans le champ prévu à cet effet, et la recherche démarre "
"immédiatement."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:817
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Search files and for content in files</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Chercher des fichiers et du contenu dans des fichiers</"
"screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:823
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Search files and for content in files</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Chercher des fichiers et du contenu dans des fichiers</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:825
#, no-c-format
msgid "&dolphin; searching files and for content in files."
msgstr "&dolphin; cherchant des fichiers et du contenu dans des fichiers."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:829
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The search is case insensitive, and does not require surrounding "
#| "wildcards (<userinput>*foo*</userinput> and <userinput>foo</userinput> "
#| "are equivalent), but you can use wildcards inside the search term. "
#| "<userinput>*</userinput> will match one or more characters, <userinput>?</"
#| "userinput> only one single character."
msgid ""
"The search is case insensitive, and does not require surrounding wildcards "
"(<userinput>*foo*</userinput> and <userinput>foo</userinput> are "
"equivalent), but you can use wildcards inside the search term. <userinput>*</"
"userinput> will match zero or more characters, <userinput>?</userinput> only "
"one single character."
msgstr ""
"La recherche est insensible à la casse et ne nécessite pas de caractères "
"joker de délimitation (<userinput>*toto*</userinput> et <userinput>toto</"
"userinput> sont équivalents), mais on peut utiliser des caractères joker "
"dans le terme à chercher. <userinput>*</userinput> correspondra à un ou "
"plusieurs caractères, <userinput>?</userinput> uniquement à un seul "
"caractère."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:833
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "This feature can be used with running nepomuk/strigi services, without "
#| "these services a KIOSlave is launched to provide the search results."
msgid ""
"This feature can be used with running Baloo services; without these services "
"a KIOSlave is launched to provide the search results."
msgstr ""
"On peut utiliser cette fonctionnalité lorsqu'on exécute des services "
"Nepomuk / Strigi. Sans ces services, un module d'E / S de KDE (KIOSlave) est "
"lancé pour fournir les résultats de la recherche."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:835
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The option from <guilabel>Everywhere</guilabel> with activated Nepomuk/"
#| "Strigi services searches in all indexed folders, without Nepomuk/Strigi "
#| "this option starts the search from the user's <replaceable>Home</"
#| "replaceable> folder."
msgid ""
"The option from <guilabel>Everywhere</guilabel> with activated Baloo "
"services searches in all indexed folders, without Baloo this option starts "
"the search from the user's <replaceable>Home</replaceable> folder."
msgstr ""
"L'option <guilabel>Partout</guilabel>, lorsque les services Nepomuk / Strigi "
"sont activés, effectue une recherche dans tous les dossiers indexés. Sans "
"Nepomuk / Strigi, cette option démarre la recherche à partir du "
"<replaceable>dossier personnel</replaceable> de l'utilisateur."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:839
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "<screeninfo>Search files and for content in files</screeninfo>"
msgid "<screeninfo>Search with More Options</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Chercher des fichiers et du contenu dans des fichiers</"
"screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:845
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "<phrase>Search files and for content in files</phrase>"
