#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:860
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is possible to clear selection using the <guibutton>Clear Selection</"
"guibutton> button."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:862
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Alternatively you can use the <link linkend=\"search-panel\">search "
#| "panel</link> to find files using Nepomuk or limit the search to selected "
#| "files."
msgid ""
"Alternatively you can use these options in the <guilabel>Places</guilabel> "
